   exclamation marks. In this paper, we propose a deep learning model
   called sAtt-BLSTM convNet that is based on the hybrid of soft
   attention-based bidirectional long short-term memory (sAtt-BLSTM) and
   convolution neural network (convNet) applying global vectors for word
   representation (GLoVe) for building semantic word embeddings. In
   addition to the feature maps generated by the sAtt-BLSTM,
