   techniques, can help in concluding that a particular video has intense
   material in it. The aim of this work is to classify social media videos
   especially related to animated cartoons with violent / nonviolent
   behaviors. It addresses the problem of content based image matching
   algorithms based on key point descriptors. The basic goal is to extract
   general information from an image without any specific query. First
   SIFT-descriptors are extracted from a large set of images. This set of
